text:
Living Marine Miscellaneous Amendments (Digital Processes) Act 2021

An Act to amend the Living Marine Resources Management Act 1995 and the Fishing (Licence Ownership and Interest) Registration Act 2001
[Royal Assent 29 November 2021]

Be it enacted by Her Excellency the Governor of Tasmania, by and with the advice and consent of the Legislative Council and House of Assembly, in Parliament assembled, as follows:

PART 1 - Preliminary

1. Short title
    This Act may be cited as the Living Marine Miscellaneous Amendments (Digital Processes) Act 2021 .

2. Commencement
    The provisions of this Act commence on a day or days to be proclaimed.

PART 2 - Living Marine Resources Management Act 1995 Amended

3.

PART 4 - Repeal of Act

29. Repeal of Act
